        "body": "Grid Layouts: Refactored the Experience section into a high-fidelity bento grid and the Fleet section into a clean 2x2 grid, ensuring consistent container widths and gaps across both.\r\nServices Page: Updated card titles to be aligned beside their icons and standardized the image hover effects to match the home page.\r\nImage Refinements: Implemented an aggressive cropping zoom fix (scale(1.1)) and object-fit: cover across the Features and Contact pages to hide internal black bars in the image assets.\r\nAsset Cleanup: Managed the deletion of old PNG assets and the addition of new specialized imagery used in the updated designs.",
