          "merged_at": "2026-03-19T06:14:59Z"
        },
        "body": "### Overview \r\nThis PR introduces the fully implemented and styled homepage for the Sk Voyage landing page. It includes comprehensive updates across all major UI sections to match exactly with the provided reference designs, a complete mobile responsiveness overhaul, and a scalable reorganisation of the underlying components hierarchy.\r\n\r\nKey Changes & Features:\r\n\r\n**UI Redesign:** Re-crafted the Contact Section (introduced a 2-column image/form layout, re-styled exact active placeholder inputs), updated the CTA Section (integrated explicit App Store/Play Store download links seamlessly), and completely reimagined the global Footer (4-column dark theme styling matching mockups, SVG hover states).\r\n\r\n**Mobile Responsiveness Engine:** Eliminated static heights (e.g. 600px blocks) and hardcoded paddings (e.g. 8rem fixed gaps) globally. Introduced clamped padding bindings, fluid font media queries wrapping massive typography, and a working mobile hamburger menu overlay inside the Navbar to prevent clipping on mobile and tablet devices.\r\n\r\n**Architecture Restructuring:** Restructured the monolithic components/sections/ and components/forms/ logic natively into a domain-driven components/home/ ecosystem. Generates empty scaffolding buckets for future pages (components/about/, components/services/, etc.), guaranteeing a clean architecture mirroring Next.js App routing.",
